_sText:
Well, I made this prefab becouse I had some spare time. 
It took me 4 days to make,and it's finally done :)
All the buildings are optimized with nodraw and area portal.
It includes a improvised overwatch tower, made by the rebels.
All the buildings are abadonded now, becouse the civil
protection came to them. Feel free to use them. Cant wait
to see my buildings in some maps that are hosted by servers
:P You can edit/modify if you want, but if you use them,
please credit my name on the authors builders of the map
(nodraw).Hope you like it.


Greetings from Holland.
